---
layout: journal.njk
lang: "en"
title: "Certified Venues"
description: "Third Place Japan certified venues in Japan. Spaces evaluated through 7 original axes and awarded certification from Certified to Flagship."
canonical: "/en/journal/certified/"
hreflang_ja: "/journal/certified/"
hreflang_en: "/en/journal/certified/"
---
<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

  <div class="mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p class="label mb-4">Certified Venues</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-light text-dark mb-4">Certified Venues in Japan</h1>
    <div class="gold-rule mb-6"></div>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted max-w-xl">
      Places certified by Third Place Japan through our 7-axis evaluation.
      Each venue is recognized not for what it serves, but for how it makes you feel.
    </p>
  </div>

  {% set enVenues = venues | venuesWithEn | sortByGrade %}
  {% if enVenues.length %}
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6" data-aos="fade-up">
    {% for v in enVenues %}
    <a href="/en/journal/certified/{{ v.slug }}/" class="venue-card block p-6 bg-white hover:bg-ivory transition-colors group">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
        <span class="grade-badge">{{ v.grade }}</span>
        <span class="label">{{ v.category }}</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-light text-dark mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">{{ v.name_en }}</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted mb-3">{{ v.area_primary.area }}, Japan</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">{{ v.citation_en }}</p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <span class="text-xs text-gold border border-gold px-2 py-0.5">{{ v.axes_primary }}</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="text-sm text-muted">English venue pages coming soon.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div>
